  "technicalDetails": "XLS (BIFF8, Binary Interchange File Format 8) is an OLE2 Compound File Binary. The Workbook stream contains BIFF8 records: BOF (beginning of file), SHEET, ROW, and MULRK records encode cell data. Each record has a 2-byte type, 2-byte length, and variable data. Formulas use RPN (Reverse Polish Notation) token arrays.",
  "completenessScore": 82
